# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# podframes — environment
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in the values. Never commit `.env.local`.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Speechbase ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Powers the multi-provider conversation audio (the star of the show).
# Gateway mode: one key routes to every TTS provider. Get it at https://speechbase.ai
SPEECHBASE_API_KEY=

# ── Google Gemini ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# One key drives the Gemini stages:
#   • text   — gemini-3.1-pro-preview           (script + b-roll cues)
#   • image  — gemini-3.1-flash-image           (Nano Banana 2 — host stills)
#   • image  — gemini-3.1-flash-lite-image      (Nano Banana 2 Lite — b-roll)
# Get it at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey   (image models require a paid key)
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# ── Replicate ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Powers the default video stage: Pruna AI p-video, audio-to-video with per-turn
# lip-sync to the real Speechbase audio. Get it at https://replicate.com/account/api-tokens
# (REPLICATE_API_TOKEN, the SDK-standard name, also works.)
REPLICATE_API_KEY=

# ── fal.ai (optional) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Alternative video stage: LTX-2.3 audio-to-video. Only needed when
# videoProvider = fal-ltx. Get it at https://fal.ai/dashboard/keys
FAL_API_KEY=

# ── Web app (optional) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Public base URL used for OG tags / share links. Defaults to http://localhost:3000
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=http://localhost:3000
